      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_20_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_20",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been absolute gold. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014runs like a dream and has been super well-loved. Whether you\u2019re commuting or heading out for a weekend getaway, this car is ready to go! It\u2019s clean, reliable, and honestly just a blast to drive. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_19_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_19",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. This example boasts a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for superior power delivery. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis longevity. The suspension utilizes refreshed bushings and upgraded dampers, maintaining the precise turn-in and feedback characteristic of this platform. While the exterior shows honest wear consistent with enthusiast use, the drivetrain remains robust and the valvetrain is exceptionally quiet. A purist-spec driver\u2019s car ready for the canyon or the track.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_16_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_16",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear. Reliable performance.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_15_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_15",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that perfectly embodies the 'good' condition standard\u2014reliable, aesthetically pleasing, and mechanically sound. The exterior paint retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals minor peppering on the hood from standard highway use. All glass is clear and free of cracks, and the alloy wheels show only very slight curb rash on the passenger side. Inside, the smoke-free cabin features supple leather upholstery with light bolstering wear on the driver's seat, while the dashboard and door panels remain free of any sun-fading or cracks. Every feature, including the panoramic sunroof, heated seats, and navigation system, is fully operational. Under the hood, the engine is clean and bone-dry, with no signs of fluid leaks. Recent service includes a fresh oil change, new air filters, and a brake fluid flush. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, ensuring you won't need a replacement any time soon. This car comes with two keys, the original owner's manual, and a thick folder of service records to prove its pedigree. It drives straight, brakes firmly, and offers a quiet, confident ride.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this expertly maintained vehicle, an ideal acquisition for the driver seeking a synthesis of performance and long-term value. This automobile has been subject to rigorous standards of care, ensuring its mechanical integrity remains beyond reproach. The interior and exterior present a refined aesthetic, reflecting a history of consistent, professional preservation. Offering a sophisticated driving experience and proven reliability, this vehicle represents a premier opportunity to secure a high-caliber asset at a competitive market valuation.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_17_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_17",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable new-to-you ride? This car has been such a joy to own and is still in wonderful shape! It's super dependable, clean, and ready to hit the road for its next big adventure. I've taken great care of it, and it runs beautifully. It's the perfect match for anyone wanting a quality car that's ready to go. Come check it out and see for yourself\u2014I'd love for it to go to a great new home!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
